s=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個係咪行規洗法？"},{"pid":"600ea5dbe275049e86745bded3a086e723cad574","tid":104200,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係用水龍頭加條長水喉<br />\n鳩射幾下就當洗左<br />\n做過清潔</blockquote><br />\n我嗰度都叫中上級商場，個地下同其他位唔濕，應該唔會咁做嘛"},{"pid":"e09de336017aa7d60b5410fb7434c285f39047f5","tid":104200,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係用水龍頭加條長水喉<br />\n鳩射幾下就當洗左<br />\n做過清潔</blockquote><br />\n我嗰度都叫中上級商場，個地下同其他位唔濕，應該唔會咁做嘛</blockquote><br />\n收工個陣先洗嫁<br />\n除非有人投訴or上頭叫洗<br />\n地下冇水係因為用水刮推走左"},{"pid":"ee40b4d8d38ce96ade22a7cd762f8ffd487a88f0","tid":104200,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實係用水龍頭加條長水喉<br />\n鳩射幾下就當洗左<br />\n做過清潔</blockquote><br />\n我嗰度都叫中上級商場，個地下同其他位唔濕，應該唔會咁做嘛</blockquote><br />\n收工個陣先洗嫁<br />\n除非有人投訴or上頭叫洗<br />\n地下冇水係因為用水刮推走左</blockquote><br />\n我聞到個陣清潔劑味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，嗰個清潔成日走入廁格偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後又鎖起一格畀自己用，但又唔記得自己鎖邊格走嚟開鳩我門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係當我狗咁撚"},{"pid":"45a90361f056dea914b660d7c67cf1e113e004dc","tid":104200,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲都拎廁紙濕水再抹。再鋪幾層廁紙晌廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da9f75b10cb82d47870d0e52eb1f44df08422cd","tid":104200,"uid":44840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"有洗未算好囉"},{"pid":"4346653d95b53ff1d1fd13c7052310d0a7ec2648","tid":104200,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都拎廁紙濕水再抹。再鋪幾層廁紙晌廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個陣都幾難擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c91dcd7183923fd6a38e1ff8c148ec97f0826","tid":104200,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有洗未算好囉</blockquote><br />\n君子所言甚是"}]}